ch.cern.dod.ws.egroups

  • Packages that use ch.cern.dod.ws.egroups 
    Package Description
    ch.cern.dod.util
    This package contains the consumer for the SOAP Web Services implemented in the DB On Demand Syscontrol project.
    ch.cern.dod.ws.egroups
    This package contains the classes generated with JAX-WS RI to consume the CERN SOAP e-group web services.
